A vintage-style technical illustration depicting a single weathered paper document floating in space, with colorful translucent geometric shapes (rectangles, squares) emerging and detaching from its surface like layers peeling away. The shapes contain abstract patterns representing different data types - swirling lines, dot matrices, gradient fills. Below the document, a ornate brass mechanical template or stencil with cutout windows hovers, casting soft shadows. The scene has warm sepia and amber tones with pops of teal and burgundy, reminiscent of 1950s technical manuals and patent drawings. Subtle paper texture throughout, with fine crosshatching details and aged edges on the document.
